            <title>[DERBY-948] Miscellaneous ResultSet methods added by JDBC 4</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-948</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As described in the JDBC 4 spec sections 16 and 3.1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This provides support for new ResultSet methods added by JDBC4 and not addressed by other JIRAs: getHoldability() and isClosed().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
